有一个<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/sonic-superstars-gives-classic-gameplay-another-modern-makeover-200643371.html">新的横向卷轴索尼克标题</a></ins>今年晚些时候推出<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/play-as-elephant-mario-in-super-mario-bros-wonder-on-october-20th-145814400.html">新的横向卷轴马里奥。</a></ins>这是什么，1991年？</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/segas-coo-says-the-company-is-not-for-sale-174334550.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/segas-coo-says-the-company-is-not-for-sale-174334550.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 0e9b8a38-87ad-4d48-b3ff-da1def712197</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 30 Jun 2023 17:43:34 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1688147015</ingested><modified> 2023-06-30T17:43:42+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Mergers, Acquisitions & Takeovers]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="2402" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-06/a8bbae70-e8f0-11ec-b3e8-65230a13efe3" width="3500"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2402" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2022-06/a8bbae70-e8f0-11ec-b3e8-65230a13efe3" width="3500"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Ki